OL,3,C'Critical diplomatic moment' as Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire deadline looms, says Cooper
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,7,Fsaid "a critical diplomatic moment" is
OL,8,Fcoming as the end of a two-week US-
OL,9,FIran ceasefire looms.
OL,11,FThe Labour Cabinet minister also again
OL,12,Fwarned that the closure of the Strait
OL,13,Fof Hormuz was "hitting the global
OL,14,Feconomy", amid international efforts
OL,15,Fto safeguard the crucial shipping
OL,16,Froute.
