OL,3,C'Critical diplomatic moment' as Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire deadline looms, says Cooper
OL,6,FShe made her comments as uncertainty
OL,7,Fhung over further talks between
OL,8,FWashington and Tehran in Pakistan
OL,9,Fbefore the fragile truce runs out on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FDoubt was cast on renewed peace
OL,13,Fnegotiations after the US seized an
OL,14,FIranian cargo ship it said was trying
OL,15,Fto run its blockade of the country's
OL,16,Fports, sparking threats of retaliation
OL,17,Ffor the "armed piracy".
OL,19,FOil prices rose again in response to
OL,20,Fthe stand-off over the strait, which
OL,21,Fis a vital trade route.
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@VO]
