OL,3,C'Critical diplomatic moment' as Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire deadline looms, says Cooper
OL,6,FSpeaking in a video posted on X, Ms
OL,7,FCooper said: "This is a critical
OL,8,Fdiplomatic moment.
OL,10,F"As we're coming to the end of the two
OL,11,Fweek agreed ceasefire on Iran,
OL,12,Fnegotiations are starting, but the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz is still closed, so
OL,14,Finternational shipping is still
OL,15,Frestricted. That is hitting the global
OL,16,Feconomy."
OL,18,FShe said she had been meeting her
OL,19,Fforeign counterparts "about the
OL,20,Fimportance of getting the Strait of
OL,21,FHormuz open again".
