OL,3,C'Critical diplomatic moment' as Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire deadline looms, says Cooper
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Donald Trump insisted he
OL,7,Fwill not be rushed into making a deal
OL,8,Fwith Iran.
OL,10,FWhile dismissing claims he was under
OL,11,Fpressure, the US president indicated
OL,12,Fan agreement would happen "relatively
OL,13,Fquickly".
OL,26,@tD@[OUuD@HO]
