OL,3,C'Critical diplomatic moment' as Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire deadline looms, says Cooper
OL,6,FHe wrote on his Truth Social platform:
OL,7,F"Time is not my adversary, the only
OL,8,Fthing that matters is that we finally,
OL,9,Fafter 47 years, straighten out the
OL,10,Fmess that other presidents let happen
OL,11,Fbecause they didn't have the courage
OL,12,For foresight to do what had to be done
OL,13,Fwith respect to Iran."
OL,15,FInsisting that the US was "winning"
OL,16,Fthe war, he pledged to keep the
OL,17,Fblockade in place until a deal was
OL,18,Freached, arguing the economic measure
OL,19,Fwas "absolutely destroying Iran".
