OL,3,C'Critical diplomatic moment' as Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire deadline looms, says Cooper
OL,6,FIran's chief negotiator and parliament
OL,7,Fspeaker Mohammed Bagher Qalibaf said
OL,8,FTehran does not enter talks in the
OL,9,Fface of threats.
OL,11,FHe accused the US president of seeking
OL,12,Fto turn the negotiating table into a
OL,13,F"table of surrender", in a post on X.
